OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry with bright or
OL,6,Fsunny spells. Chance of some well
OL,7,Fscattered showers developing
OL,8,Fthroughout the day, although these
OL,9,Fwill be less heavy than on Thursday.
OL,10,FBreezy along coasts. Slightly milder
OL,11,Finland than recent days.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny showers fading to leave a
OL,14,Flargely dry night, with lengthy clear
OL,15,Fspells. Chance of a few coastal
OL,16,Fshowers. Turning chilly, with patchy
OL,17,Ffrost in prone rural spots. Light
OL,18,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
