OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FLargely dry and bright,
OL,6,Fafter a chilly start. However, cloud
OL,7,Fwill increase from the west during the
OL,8,Fafternoon, which will bring some
OL,9,Foutbreaks of rain by evening. Light
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FEarly
OL,13,Frain clearing to give largely dry and
OL,14,Fbright conditions on Sunday. Sunny
OL,15,Fspells and showers, locally heavy, on
OL,16,FMonday. Wet and windy conditions
OL,17,Fspread east Tuesday. Temperatures near
OL,18,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
